cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about a toolkit for machine reading comprehension, which involves natural language processing, artificial intelligence, and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers topics related to natural language processing and computational linguistics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which are all relevant to the development of machine comprehension models.
